{"tid":501597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冒6°C低溫登大帽山 露營師生： 好似雪條咁凍","createTime":"2017-12-17T04:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T07:41:57.000Z","uid":84436,"like":12,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d33f8a2d0daba5ae4f28afb12d630808fc0dc6","tid":501597,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T04:30:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171216/57591070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57591070&d=C9rODD4zZtdGQ3sn10KX3wKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=c56d0fd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57591070&h=a064536b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171216/57591070</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天文台今午發出入冬後首個寒冷天氣警告，晚上10時大帽山錄得2.4&deg;C低溫，料隨後兩三日早上寒冷，最低氣溫維持在12&deg;C或以下。《蘋果》晚上到大帽山，溫度計顯示為6&deg;C，另外不少市民專程登山感受寒意。<br />\n<br />\n梁Sir今日帶領數名小學生在帽山附近露營，晚上與學生一同上大帽雷達站行夜山，他指山上「大風好凍」。跟隨梁Sir上山的周同學稱，雖然穿了5件衫加晍包保暖，但上完山頂後覺得「好似雪條咁凍」，但落山時與朋友一同跑步暖身，所以出了一身汗。<br />\n另外，吳同學友稱，今日未知會登大帽山，但已穿了4件衫保暖，但仍感覺山頂「好凍好凍，雪櫃咁凍」，他直言過程「唔好玩，太凍啦」。"},{"pid":"03b392e0afb8e777f17d71b14132dad565a03243","tid":501597,"uid":16676,"like":187,"dislike":6,"score":181,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"登山感受寒意<br />\n<br />\n家下做乜撚野遮, 食飽飯無屎屙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff382d000b9d9db1316eef636042c21a15e90202","tid":501597,"uid":67237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T04:35:33.000Z","msg":"幾時又要人救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd673cbf4ff632a5f5e7501eec17231336083377","tid":5